title: [Zee's Outfitting]
description: Enclosed by knotty pine walls, the shop features a brass flowerpot in the center of its strewn pine floor.  A glass-eyed spotted gak head hangs under the wooden ceiling.  Right near the front is an etched brass bin and a gilded maple table.

A glass-eyed spotted gak head hangs on one of the knotty pine walls, and an uneven wooden ceiling rises overhead.  A brass flowerpot sits in one corner of a sawdust strewn pine floor.  There is a gilded maple table on one side of the shop and an etched brass bin on the other.
